title: #104: The Paranormal with  Karen Rontowski and Kira Soltanovich
description: Thank you everyone for tuning into another cosmic comedic journey in to the paranormal with today's guests Kira Soltanovich and Karen Rontowski hosts of  the "Karen & Kira Can Read" podcast. Both are funny comedians and veterans in the realms of physic abilities and the reading of the Tarot card deck. We talk ghosts, jinn, dark entities, the Vortex that exists at The World Famous Comedy Store, spirit possession, empaths, Indigo children and Sam gets his Tarot read.
